  description: "concurrent.futures.FIRST_COMPLETED.__class__.__name__ == 'str' — FIRST_COMPLETED is a plain str constant, not an enum member; its value is the string 'FIRST_COMPLETED'; new to concurrent_futures_extra208; verified Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  category: constant_type
