  description: "concurrent.futures.wait.__code__.co_varnames.__len__() == 7 — wait() has 7 local variable slots: ('fs', 'timeout', 'return_when', 'f', 'done', 'not_done', 'waiter'); new to concurrent_futures_extra208; verified Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  category: code_introspection
